description: The construction of a new Government Hospital in the Salfeet District of the West Bank was an important priorty of the Palestinian Authority to meet the general health needs of the public of the district.

subproject.corporate outcome: Expansion and access to financial services for the poor, employment and income generation and access to markets, goods and services.
subproject.description: This project fulfilled the priority needs of the Palestinian Authority to construct a  Governmental Hospital in the Salfeet District. The hospital provides emergency room, in patient, maternity, general surgery, lab, pharmacy, pediatric, and other services to the general public.
subproject.title: Construction of Salfeet Hosp.

title: Construction of the Salfeet Government Hospital
